Use the arrow keys to move Floppa (the Brown Cat) around to collect the rainbow shrimp.
Make sure to avoid the evil Blue, Red, and Green Popcats because they want to destroy you!

There are 3 levels, slow, fast, and faster. You must complete all 3 before the time runs out and the game is over.

Note: There are 209 shrimps >:^)

Flop speed = 160
